Package com.rb.biz.guice

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    RBClock
    Tells us what time it is.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    RBClockModifier
    Lets you modify the RBClock.
    RBClockModifier.RBClockModifierToken
    Unusually, this class holds nothing and does nothing.
    RBSimpleTestClock
    A simple RBClock that just stores a LocalDateTime and doesn't do any tricks with pre-generating thread-local clocks like RBThreadLocalClock does.
    RBThreadLocalClock
    A RBClock that's particularly useful when running multiple backtests in parallel.
